WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:01.679
Good morning family.

00:00:01.679 --> 00:00:03.737
Thank you for joining us today.

00:00:03.737 --> 00:00:05.560
Well, it's Brandon and Diana again.

00:00:06.580 --> 00:00:18.903
I think the last two videos about the trafficking and the one before that about all the things the Lord has been showing me have been heavy.

00:00:19.634 --> 00:00:29.662
It's interesting because I'm letting you all into my private prayer time teaching because the Lord told me, 'I want you to be real and I want you to teach my people to pray.

00:00:29.662 --> 00:00:36.920
' The only way I know how to teach you all, because I asked the Lord how to teach people to pray, is by demonstration.

00:00:36.920 --> 00:00:40.590
Diana and I—I'm not a teacher.

00:00:40.590 --> 00:00:53.556
I don't really know what that means other than I just keep coming on here and teaching you, showing you by example how I pray every day and how I've been doing it for years.

00:00:55.400 --> 00:00:58.480
I don't feel like there's a wrong way, a right way, or a perfect way.

00:01:01.942 --> 00:01:08.700
This is just how I do it, and obviously I get results, so I feel like I'm on the right road.

00:01:08.700 --> 00:01:18.937
Not saying that everything I do is right or perfect, but I seek the Lord and he told me that the end is coming soon.

00:01:18.937 --> 00:01:22.011
Do you understand the end of all things?

00:01:22.011 --> 00:01:23.440
This dispensation of grace.

00:01:23.800 --> 00:01:35.733
People go, 'Well, you see these things and you pray over these things,' and I told you all I don't feel that I'm a prophetic watchman in the sense that I see future things to pray about.

00:01:35.733 --> 00:01:40.210
Am I like some of these guys on Sid Roth or whatever?

00:01:40.210 --> 00:01:43.771
No, I don't feel like I am.

00:01:44.119 --> 00:01:48.826
Obviously, I'm doing exactly what he's told me to do.

00:01:48.826 --> 00:01:51.040
I don't know what that really entails.

00:01:51.040 --> 00:01:54.680
All I know is that he's told me to go up higher.

00:01:55.320 --> 00:02:00.095
Yesterday and today, I said, 'What does that look like?

00:02:00.095 --> 00:02:03.280
How do you go higher with prayer?

00:02:03.280 --> 00:02:05.129
How do you go into a different realm?

00:02:05.129 --> 00:02:15.233
' I've listened to every prayer person that this generation has to offer—more than once, hundreds of times actually.

00:02:15.233 --> 00:02:31.030
All day long, I listen to something and feed my spirit with my headset on or on my phone, driving in the car or whatever, seeking the teaching to get me to the next level.

00:02:31.599 --> 00:02:32.800
Diana and I even said it today.

00:02:32.800 --> 00:02:36.434
She goes, 'What does that look like, Braden?

00:02:39.580 --> 00:02:43.618
We're wanting to grab onto something that we have no clue what we're grabbing onto.

00:02:43.618 --> 00:02:52.056
' The only one that knows is the Holy Spirit, and he keeps telling us to go higher.

00:02:52.056 --> 00:02:57.627
There's something major about to take place—a major shaking to awaken.

00:02:57.627 --> 00:03:04.260
I know that Jesus Christ is coming and he's coming soon.

00:03:04.260 --> 00:03:17.173
The only way the manifestation of what we're believing for—for the outpouring of the coming of the Lord, the glorious church, the bride—will be birthed out of prayer.

00:03:17.173 --> 00:03:33.063
From stopping sex trafficking to wars and rumors of wars, protecting our loved ones, being in the right place at the right time—it's all birthed out of prayer.

00:03:33.063 --> 00:03:40.950
Without prayer, I don't believe it's going to manifest like we want it to.

00:03:40.950 --> 00:03:55.780
Even with the wealth transfer, the things I've seen about the wealth transfer—seeking him, like he said, 'Seek me and lose yourself in him by seeking him and you will find him'—so he can trust you with it.

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:02.249
He needs to trust you with that wealth transfer like he was showing us in prayer the other day.

00:04:02.249 --> 00:04:16.959
Not seeking the money, not seeking for crypto to go up or whatever, but falling in love with him and listening to him because he'll tell you.

00:04:16.959 --> 00:04:24.590
Seeking his face and you can have what is in his hand, just like he said: 'Seek my face.

00:04:24.590 --> 00:04:28.195
You want what's in my hand?

00:04:28.195 --> 00:04:38.617
' But the money is so shallow; falling in love with him is coming up higher to another level with him.

00:04:38.617 --> 00:04:49.040
People go, 'Well, you've seen all this stuff—the stock market crash, the water shortages, and food shortages—well, when is that going to happen?

00:04:49.040 --> 00:04:52.839
' I said, 'I have no clue.

00:05:09.428 --> 00:05:09.800
All I know is I feel an urgency.

00:05:09.800 --> 00:05:17.056
' As watchmen, as Diana and I pray and watch, we see these things coming.

00:05:17.056 --> 00:05:26.089
We know it gets closer and closer every day, or we're pushing against it in prayer.

00:05:26.089 --> 00:05:38.760
We're coming against these things and saying, 'Thus far, no further, Satan,' but some things will take place because we are in the last of the last days.

00:05:41.067 --> 00:05:48.160
He said we would have plagues and pestilence, wars and rumors of wars, droughts and shortages.

00:05:56.960 --> 00:05:57.160
We'll have fearful sights in the heavenlies.

00:05:59.880 --> 00:06:06.480
He said we would have all that, but the Bible says that he has never seen the righteous forsaken or his seed begging bread.

00:06:18.069 --> 00:06:18.423
That was David.

00:06:18.423 --> 00:06:22.974
If that is in the Word, that's for me.

00:06:22.974 --> 00:06:41.880
If he said, 'I will walk through the valley of the shadow of death and I'll fear no evil,' that means no matter what is going on, there's going to be some stuff going on.

00:06:49.080 --> 00:06:58.000
If he told me that we've got to get Psalms 91 and Psalms 23 down inside of you like a pillar—he said if it is not, the devourer is going to eat your lunch, basically.

00:06:58.000 --> 00:07:04.365
The Word is the foundation of everything we are as Christians—the believer.

00:07:04.982 --> 00:07:10.840
It's through the Word that we'll know the truth and the truth will set us free.

00:07:15.080 --> 00:07:15.460
I saw the storms coming.

00:07:15.460 --> 00:07:24.330
I've seen major storms coming on the East Coast and now I'm seeing them on the West Coast.

00:07:36.423 --> 00:07:37.900
Now I'm seeing a storm, but I'm seeing a Goshen, a beautiful area of revival throughout America, throughout these places that will be places of refuge for the body of Christ.

00:07:37.900 --> 00:07:41.639
They will be places of great Holy Ghost and fire.

00:07:41.639 --> 00:07:47.289
People say, 'Well, when is all this going to happen?

00:07:47.289 --> 00:08:05.056
' I have a clue of what I feel in my spirit, but I have learned: do not quote time frames because it will catch your hand in the door.

00:08:05.056 --> 00:08:06.529
Just pray.

00:08:06.529 --> 00:08:09.980
None of the other stuff matters.

00:08:09.980 --> 00:08:23.720
If you seek him, you'll find him, and he will show you and tell you, 'Sister so-and-so, you need to go and do this,' because you're staying in sync with him.

00:08:23.720 --> 00:08:26.989
You're dancing; he's leading, you follow.

00:08:26.989 --> 00:08:28.239
It's a dance.

00:08:28.239 --> 00:08:30.600
Prayer is a dance, like I told you all.

00:08:33.099 --> 00:08:51.280
In that, he'll say, 'Hey, today it's a good idea for you to go and get 20 cans of green beans' or a big bag of rice, or, 'Today is a day that I really want you to start seeking out a well for your property.

00:08:51.280 --> 00:08:54.365
' If he doesn't speak to you, do not move.

00:08:56.651 --> 00:09:01.120
I went and started buying stuff and the rats found it; the mice find it too and now they're eating all my stuff.

00:09:01.120 --> 00:09:07.600
It's not for the cankerworm to eat all the stuff.

00:09:07.600 --> 00:09:12.228
If you're moved out of fear or emotion, you will miss it.

00:09:12.228 --> 00:09:18.360
But if you're staying in a dance with him, you will find him.

00:09:18.360 --> 00:09:30.680
Maybe he's just telling you to start educating yourself about things like food prep, how to preserve your food, and how to store your food.

00:09:30.680 --> 00:09:41.280
If we know in part and we see in part, let's pray for the whole part.

00:09:41.280 --> 00:09:46.265
Diana said it last time: it's like a puzzle piece.

00:09:46.265 --> 00:09:51.389
We pray over the puzzle piece we know we have in our hand.

00:09:51.389 --> 00:09:57.320
We look at the puzzle and ask, 'Where do I put my puzzle piece?

00:09:57.320 --> 00:10:01.093
Where does that puzzle piece fit?

00:10:01.093 --> 00:10:11.539
' As I find the puzzle piece, I don't just put it down; I pray it through.

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:18.940
You pray it through, and God will give you another puzzle piece.

00:10:20.460 --> 00:10:25.360
You get it in your hand and ask, 'Where does that puzzle piece fit?

00:10:25.360 --> 00:10:29.219
' Until you see the picture, do not move.

00:10:29.219 --> 00:10:32.160
You'll get piece after piece after piece.

00:10:35.073 --> 00:10:36.068
The last three times it's been a different piece.

00:10:36.068 --> 00:10:40.502
He's wanted me to pray over the trafficking, the wars, and all kinds of things.

00:10:44.662 --> 00:10:44.948
I don't even remember some of the things.

00:10:46.342 --> 00:10:47.760
I'm just like, 'Wow, this has been...

00:10:47.760 --> 00:10:57.105
' I told Braden, who edits the videos—that's why I know he's memorized them—because it takes him time and he listens to it over and over again.

00:10:57.105 --> 00:11:20.473
But I just know this: being filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit, you won't miss out on what you're supposed to have, when you're supposed to have it, and how much you're supposed to have—all of it—because you're staying in sync with him.

00:11:20.473 --> 00:11:32.578
He may tell you something different than the guy in California; he could have a different word than the guy in New York.

00:11:49.320 --> 00:11:49.645
No word is going to be cookie-cutter for every individual person.

00:11:49.645 --> 00:11:52.340
We're all uniquely and wonderfully made.

00:12:04.347 --> 00:12:04.693
And he's going to tell us something different than my friend down the road.

00:12:04.693 --> 00:12:13.120
He could tell this person, "I want you to invest in this and this and this," and then the other person goes, "Well, I never heard that.

00:12:22.560 --> 00:12:26.880
I don't feel like I'm supposed to do that.

00:12:26.880 --> 00:12:31.760
" Well, should I do that?

00:12:31.760 --> 00:12:32.240
No.

00:12:32.240 --> 00:12:36.137
Only do what he tells you to do.

00:12:36.137 --> 00:12:42.853
That's what Jesus said: "I only do what the Father tells me to do.

00:12:42.853 --> 00:12:44.354
" That is a perfect plan.

00:12:44.354 --> 00:12:46.491
Well, I don't hear him.

00:12:46.491 --> 00:12:49.240
Well, it's time for you to learn.

00:12:49.240 --> 00:12:50.434
Get your Bible.

00:12:50.434 --> 00:12:53.490
Read the Bible until it becomes real to you.

00:12:53.490 --> 00:12:55.760
Find a passage.

00:12:55.760 --> 00:12:57.897
Find verses like Diana reads.

00:12:57.897 --> 00:13:00.560
Diana—I've never seen anybody read her Bible like this woman does.

00:13:00.560 --> 00:13:13.599
This woman reads her Bible, and she'll sit there and highlight and outline and do everything; she's continually feeding on the Word of God, reading it because it's becoming real to her.

00:13:14.560 --> 00:13:17.618
And she goes, "Brandon, I've never seen this before.

00:13:28.240 --> 00:13:28.560
" And I'm like, "How did you never see that before?

00:13:28.560 --> 00:13:31.253
You've read that like five times.

00:13:31.253 --> 00:13:34.089
" but she says, "I read something new today.

00:13:34.347 --> 00:13:37.725
" And I'm like, "Wow, but you've read that so many times, baby.

00:13:37.725 --> 00:13:40.626
" But today she got something new.

00:13:56.160 --> 00:13:56.520
And she's in there telling me, "Look what I got today, Brandon.

00:14:05.440 --> 00:14:05.720
I got something new today.

00:14:05.720 --> 00:14:13.136
" and she's sitting there reading it to me and I'm like, "Yeah, that is new.

00:14:24.577 --> 00:14:24.926
It's new.

00:14:27.400 --> 00:14:27.759
The Bible's alive.

00:14:27.759 --> 00:14:32.645
The Word of God is alive.

00:14:32.645 --> 00:14:35.008
" That means it's always changing.

00:14:35.008 --> 00:14:36.600
You know why?

00:14:36.600 --> 00:14:38.800
Because you're changing.

00:14:50.840 --> 00:14:53.128
And the way you heard it today will be different than the way you will hear it tomorrow, because we're going from glory to glory to glory.

00:15:19.479 --> 00:15:19.679
And the Word of God is alive and is able to change you as you get in the Word.

00:15:20.080 --> 00:15:35.543
And what you saw a year ago will be totally different than what you see tomorrow because we're changing.

00:15:35.543 --> 00:15:44.440
That's why I try to tell you all: my job is never to teach fear.

00:15:44.440 --> 00:15:49.587
It's never to scare you and go, "Oh, no.

00:15:49.587 --> 00:16:00.494
" Because I've told you I don't feel fear about it; I don't feel fear about any of this.

00:16:12.787 --> 00:16:13.293
I pray about it.

00:16:13.293 --> 00:16:26.300
So, I don't want to ramble, but I just want to encourage you all to get in that beautiful book.

00:16:26.300 --> 00:16:32.784
Get in that Bible and let it become life to you.

00:16:32.784 --> 00:16:42.216
Breathe in those pages spiritually as you read it and just sit there.

00:16:42.216 --> 00:16:48.480
Find a translation that ministers to you.

00:16:48.480 --> 00:16:54.820
So many people get so stuck on it having to be King James.

00:16:56.169 --> 00:17:00.942
And if it's not King James, it's not the real Word.

00:17:11.671 --> 00:17:12.000
And I'm like, "But that doesn't minister to me.

00:17:12.000 --> 00:17:17.760
" I don't understand these "thees" and "thous" and all that.

00:17:17.760 --> 00:17:20.400
I'm just an old country boy.

00:17:26.080 --> 00:17:26.347
I say, "Tell me something that I understand.

00:17:32.640 --> 00:17:34.640
" If not, it isn't getting inside of you and you're wasting your time because the truth you know will set you free.

00:17:34.640 --> 00:17:42.658
If you aren't knowing it and it isn't getting inside of you, you aren't getting free.

00:17:42.658 --> 00:17:48.172
But people want to get all religious and stuff.

00:17:48.172 --> 00:17:53.400
I just go, "Hey, there isn't any religion in this house.

00:18:02.000 --> 00:18:02.360
We just want to be real with Jesus.

00:18:02.360 --> 00:18:03.080
Relationship.

00:18:03.080 --> 00:18:04.784
It's about relationship.

00:18:06.344 --> 00:18:07.611
And we want to love Jesus.

00:18:10.187 --> 00:18:21.305
" And when he tells us, "Brandon, I want you to go to a different, higher level," I'm going, "God, teach me how to get there because I want more of you.

00:18:28.916 --> 00:18:29.200
I want to know you.

00:18:35.407 --> 00:18:36.160
" And that's why we get so excited.

00:18:36.160 --> 00:18:39.840
We go to Billy Burke meetings.

00:18:39.840 --> 00:18:44.400
We go to them because we get something out of those meetings.

00:18:44.400 --> 00:18:50.251
If I can go to another Billy Burke service at least one more time this year, or two more times...

00:18:50.251 --> 00:18:55.644
Because that's what Diana does—we're always strategizing: where is he going to be?

00:18:55.644 --> 00:18:58.453
Because he doesn't put a big schedule out.

00:19:03.421 --> 00:19:03.670
And we're always like, "Show us, Lord.

00:19:19.319 --> 00:19:19.699
" Because if he can be in this, we will put our money aside and be able to go and be a part of that.

00:19:19.699 --> 00:19:26.133
Even if it's just a day, there's something about sitting in that anointing in the atmosphere.

00:19:26.133 --> 00:19:31.840
If I find somebody else that's similar to it, I'll follow them, too.

00:19:31.840 --> 00:19:38.738
It's not just about Billy Burke, y'all.

00:19:38.738 --> 00:19:40.190
It's the glory.

00:19:42.504 --> 00:19:42.832
I don't know Billy Burke well.

00:19:42.832 --> 00:19:49.653
I've talked to him like two or three times and once on the phone.

00:19:49.653 --> 00:19:58.260
He'll text me every once in a while and say, "I'm praying for you.

00:19:58.260 --> 00:20:00.907
" He's a nice man.

00:20:00.907 --> 00:20:11.656
But it's not about Billy Burke because I don't know him outside of the glory.

00:20:11.656 --> 00:20:15.029
It's just wanting to be around the anointing.

00:20:15.714 --> 00:20:16.660
Do you understand?

00:20:16.660 --> 00:20:17.440
It's anybody.

00:20:17.440 --> 00:20:19.880
It wouldn't matter who it was.

00:20:19.880 --> 00:20:27.919
If I can experience the glory, I want to be there.

00:20:44.000 --> 00:20:45.679
It doesn't matter what service it is.

00:20:45.679 --> 00:20:56.181
I just want him because it's not Billy Burke that I'm after; it's the glory that I'm after.

00:21:03.520 --> 00:21:03.840
It's just him.

00:21:07.697 --> 00:21:12.750
And if I can seek him and find him, it will change my life forever.

00:21:12.750 --> 00:21:15.914
In his presence, there's fullness of joy.

00:21:15.914 --> 00:21:20.550
In his presence, there's fullness of peace.

00:21:35.989 --> 00:21:36.179
In him, he can change my circumstances of everything I've ever been broke, busted, and disgusted about.

00:21:36.179 --> 00:21:43.580
He'll change it in an instant if I can just touch his hem.

00:21:43.580 --> 00:21:49.120
But I'm willing to do whatever it takes to get there.

00:21:49.120 --> 00:21:51.940
One second, one thread—that's all it takes.

00:21:51.940 --> 00:22:03.130
Whenever the Lord visits our house and it's real and it's tangible to me and Diana and Braden, Paisley, my little girl, there's just nothing like it.

00:22:03.130 --> 00:22:06.213
I never rush whenever he comes.

00:22:06.213 --> 00:22:19.700
When you have those visitations in your car and you're sitting there weeping and you just sit and go, "In your presence there is fullness of joy.

00:22:20.720 --> 00:22:26.830
" And I know there's so many of you today that are so desperate.

00:22:26.830 --> 00:22:29.084
I see the photos.

00:22:29.084 --> 00:22:36.750
There's so many we can't even put them on the table anymore.

00:22:36.760 --> 00:22:40.760
There's so much need.

00:22:40.760 --> 00:22:46.663
There's so much brokenness, isn't there, baby?

00:22:50.640 --> 00:22:50.880
We weep.

00:22:51.120 --> 00:23:00.830
The man that says, "I'm embarrassed because I cannot tell the deacon or the people at the church that I battle with alcoholism because if I do, they'll criticize me.

00:23:01.290 --> 00:23:04.319
" And I thought, "Oh, but I want to be free.

00:23:04.319 --> 00:23:07.807
" He says he has nine children.

00:23:08.700 --> 00:23:17.820
The pressure of life will drive a man to drink, but you're trying to fill the void that only Jesus can fill.

00:23:17.820 --> 00:23:18.960
Alcohol will just drive and kill you.

00:23:18.960 --> 00:23:19.860
I've seen it.

00:23:19.860 --> 00:23:20.860
Pickle your liver.

00:23:20.860 --> 00:23:22.240
My relative did it.

00:23:22.240 --> 00:23:23.383
Died of alcoholism.

00:23:29.400 --> 00:23:29.710
I saw it right there.

00:23:29.710 --> 00:23:30.640
Killed him.

00:23:34.400 --> 00:23:42.149
And all it is is you think, "If I just get one little sip, it will help numb the issues of my life with this alcohol.

00:23:42.149 --> 00:24:01.538
" But then the devil opens the door when you open a little crack and you let him in by just a little bit of this, a little bit of that, and he takes a mile.

00:24:11.679 --> 00:24:20.106
And the next thing you know, he has a noose around your neck and he's pulling you down in that pit and you say, "Oh, I don't know how to get out.

00:24:20.106 --> 00:24:22.240
What do I do now?

00:24:29.247 --> 00:24:29.912
" and you can't tell your pastor.

00:24:29.912 --> 00:24:36.533
This whole letter broke me today because I said, "That's it.

00:24:36.533 --> 00:24:38.363
This is it.

00:24:38.363 --> 00:24:40.731
This is why we're on YouTube.

00:24:49.919 --> 00:24:50.150
" We pray for you, you and your beautiful nine children.

00:24:50.150 --> 00:24:51.306
My goodness, sir.

00:25:02.187 --> 00:25:02.453
You have so many beautiful children.

00:25:10.209 --> 00:25:10.559
They need you.

00:25:14.934 --> 00:25:28.271
And the Lord wants you free from alcoholism, not for you to be ashamed and embarrassed.

00:27:25.051 --> 00:27:28.430
We don't run away from God when we sin; we run to him.

00:27:32.640 --> 00:27:55.179
And if you can't run to your people without them judging you and being judgmental and hurting you, I'd find a new church because that's not a place I want to go.

00:27:55.749 --> 00:28:44.470
I would find a church that will help me, that will teach me the word and teach me how to get free.

00:28:44.480 --> 00:29:00.349
But I'm glad you're here.

00:29:00.349 --> 00:29:02.546
Diana is glad you're here.

00:29:02.999 --> 00:29:04.153
We pray for you.

00:29:04.153 --> 00:29:12.232
I seriously went before your photo.

00:29:12.232 --> 00:29:20.270
Your family is beautiful and God has a plan for your life, sir.

00:29:20.270 --> 00:29:32.720
It is not for you to walk in alcoholism; it is not for you to feel why you turned to it in the first place.

00:29:32.720 --> 00:29:57.440
You have a lot of mouths to feed and a lot of responsibility; nine kids is a lot.

00:29:57.440 --> 00:30:00.479
But every single one of them...

00:30:15.858 --> 00:30:43.917
